name: R2_dicom_dcim_for_R5
title: Cross-version VS for R2.DICOM Controlled Terminology Definitions for use in FHIR R5
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/dicom-dcim|01 for use in FHIR R5. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R2 to R5.
